videos.headline: Smith makes a man miss and goes in for the Texas TD
videos.description: Jake Smith gets a 10-yard touchdown pass from Sam Ehlinger to extend the Longhorns' lead against Kansas.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Smith makes a man miss and goes in for the Texas TD) 2019/10/19 ESHEET

videos.headline: Longhorns score 1st against the Jayhawks
videos.description: Roschon Johnson rushes through the small gap up the middle almost untouched for 14 yards for a Texas touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Longhorns score 1st against the Jayhawks) 2019/10/19 ESHEET

videos.headline: Pooka dashes through traffic for Kansas TD
videos.description: Pooka Williams Jr. takes the ball up the middle for a 7-yard contested touchdown for the Jayhawks' first of the game.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Pooka dashes through traffic for Kansas TD) 2019/10/19 ESHEET

videos.headline: Jayhawks take 1st lead in Austin since 1997
videos.description: Carter Stanley throws a short 7-yard pass to Takulve Williams to give Kansas a 17-14 advantage, the Jayhawks' first lead in 22 years at Texas.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Jayhawks take 1st lead in Austin since 1997) 2019/10/19 ESHEET

videos.headline: Eagles fights off Jayhawks defender to score
videos.description: Sam Ehlinger finds Brennan Eagles in the end zone with a 5-yard pass for another Texas touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Eagles fights off Jayhawks defender to score) 2019/10/19 ESHEET

videos.headline: Robinson holds on for Kansas TD
videos.description: Stephon Robinson keeps the loosely caught ball away from his Texas defender and scores the nine-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Robinson holds on for Kansas TD) 2019/10/19 ESHEET

videos.headline: Duvernay jogs into the end zone for Texas
videos.description: Sam Ehlinger throws the quick short pass to Devin Duvernay who easily runs it in for a 14-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Duvernay jogs into the end zone for Texas) 2019/10/19 ESHEET

videos.headline: Jamison runs it back for a Texas defensive PAT
videos.description: After the PAT is blocked by Malcolm Roach, D'Shawn Jamison catches it and scores the Longhorns' first defensive PAT since 2016.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Jamison runs it back for a Texas defensive PAT) 2019/10/18 ESHEET

videos.headline: Longhorns' Ehlinger links up with Duvernay again
videos.description: Texas' Sam Ehlinger launches a 43-yard pass to Devin Duvernay for their second touchdown of the game.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Longhorns' Ehlinger links up with Duvernay again) 2019/10/19 ESHEET

videos.headline: Stanley finds Parchment as Kansas ties it at 40-40
videos.description: Carter Stanley gets the ball into the hands of Andrew Parchment who scores an 11-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Stanley finds Parchment as Kansas ties it at 40-40) 2019/10/19 ESHEET

videos.headline: Texas' Ingram pushes his way to the end zone
videos.description: Not long after Kansas ties the game, Keaontay Ingram battles to put Texas ahead 47-40.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Texas' Ingram pushes his way to the end zone) 2019/10/19 ESHEET

videos.headline: Kansas takes late lead on TD, 2-point conversion
videos.description: Carter Stanley connects with Stephon Robinson for the 22-yard touchdown, then finds Daylon Charlot open in the end zone for the 2-point conversion to take the 48-47 lead over Texas.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Kansas takes late lead on TD, 2-point conversion) 2019/10/19 ESHEET
